update.name: CVE-2024-39090-PoC
update.description: This PoC script exploits CVE-2024-39090, a CSRF to Stored XSS vulnerability in PHPGurukul Online Shopping Portal v2.0. It automates CSRF attacks to inject persistent JavaScript payloads, which execute when a privileged user accesses the affected page, enabling actions such as session hijacking or credential theft.
